1.Gambaran Sistem
Sistem Water Truck Controller adalah pengendali mikro berbasis Arduino Nano untuk mengelola sistem penyemprotan air pada kendaraan tangki. 
Sistem ini mengontrol:  

    3 Sprayer (Kiri, Tengah, Kanan)
    Water Pump (Pompa Air)
    Intermittent Mode (Automatis ON/OFF)
    Monitoring KPI (Jam Operasi & Jarak Semprot)
    Penyimpanan Konfigurasi di FRAM FM24C64
    Display LCD 16x2 untuk informasi real-time
    RTC DS3231 untuk waktu (opsional)

Hardware Configuration
Pin Definitions (constants.h)
Output Pins (Relay)
cpp
#define RELAY_SPRAYER_RH        9   // Sprayer Kanan
#define RELAY_SPRAYER_CENTER    12  // Sprayer Tengah
#define RELAY_SPRAYER_LH        11  // Sprayer Kiri
#define RELAY_ROTARY            6   // Lampu Rotary
#define RELAY_AUTO_MAN_IND      7   // Indikator Mode Auto
#define RELAY_WORKING_LAMP      8   // Lampu Kerja
#define RELAY_WATER_PUMP        10  // Pompa Air
#define PIN_MOSFET_GATE         13  // Kontrol PWM Valve
#define RELAY_WATER_LEVEL_ALARM 4   // Alarm Level Air (opsional)
Input Pins
cpp
#define PIN_THROTTLE_PEDAL      A6  // Pedal Throttle (Analog)
#define PIN_TIMER_POT           A7  // Potensiometer Timer (Analog)
#define BUTTON_SPRAYER_RH       A0  // Tombol Sprayer Kanan
#define BUTTON_SPRAYER_CENTER   A1  // Tombol Sprayer Tengah
#define BUTTON_SPRAYER_LH       A2  // Tombol Sprayer Kiri
#define PIN_ENGINE_RUNNING      A3  // Sensor Engine Running
#define PIN_SPEED_SENSOR        2   // Sensor Kecepatan (Interrupt)
#define PIN_WATER_LEVEL         3   // Sensor Level Air (Digital)
I2C Addresses
cpp
#define LCD_I2C_ADDRESS         0x27    // LCD 16x2
#define RTC_I2C_ADDRESS         0x68    // DS3231
#define FRAM_I2C_ADDRESS        0x50    // FM24C64
