State Machine Sistem
text
                    ┌─────────────┐
                    │   IDLE      │
                    │ (Tanki OK)  │
                    └──────┬──────┘
                           │
              ┌────────────┼────────────┐
              │            │            │
              ▼            ▼            ▼
       ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐
       │ MANUAL   │ │ AUTO     │ │ EMERGENCY│
       │ (Sprayer)│ │ (Interm) │ │ (Locked) │
       └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘
              │            │            │
              └────────────┼────────────┘
                           │
                           ▼
                    ┌─────────────┐
                    │ ENGINE      │
                    │ MONITORING  │
                    └─────────────┘
Alur Penyimpanan Data
text
Engine Running
    ↓
Update RAM Cache (cachedKPI) ──→ Update setiap detik
    ↓
IF (elapsed ≥ 1 jam) ──→ FLUSH ke FRAM
    ↓
Engine Stopped / Emergency
    ↓
FORCE WRITE ke FRAM (save semua data)
Spesifikasi Teknis
Parameter	Nilai
Mikrokontroler	Arduino Nano (ATmega328P)
Frekuensi	16 MHz
Tegangan	12V (Relay) / 5V (Logika)
I2C Speed	400 kHz
FRAM	FM24C64 (8KB)
RTC	DS3231
LCD	16x2 I2C
Jumlah Relay	7 (SPST)
MOSFET Gate	PWM 8-bit (0-255)
Input Analog	2 (Throttle, Potensiometer)
Input Digital	4 (Tombol, Sensor)
Interrupt	1 (Speed Sensor)


