Modul-modul kunci:

ConfigManager – Manajemen konfigurasi & KPI
ButtonManager – Deteksi tombol (Short/Long/Kombinasi)
IntermittentManager – Mode auto ON/OFF
WaterLevelManager – Safety interlock air
FRAMManager – Penyimpanan eksternal via I2C

